Expression
public final class SqrtExpression
extends AbstractSingleEncapsulatedExpression

The SQRT function takes a numeric argument and returns a double.

JPA 1.0, 2.0:

BNF: expression ::= SQRT(simple_arithmetic_expression)

JPA 2.1:

BNF: expression ::= SQRT(arithmetic_expression)

2.4
Author:
Pascal Filion
